data.description: Welcome to 989 Van Buren Avenue, a beautifully updated 4 bedroom cape located in Franklin Square. The property is located on a beautiful tree-lined street and perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The first floor features an entry foyer, spacious living room, dining room, large eat-in kitchen, office area, 2 bedrooms and a full bath. The second floor has 2 generous-sized bedrooms. Some highlights of the home include an updated kitchen with newer appliances, in-ground sprinklers, 2-zone heat, new oil burner and a finished basement. The private backyard with rear patio make it perfect for entertaining or summer BBQs. This home has incredible curb appeal and in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, schools and the park. Don't miss this one!
